snippet: LEAD: Puzzled scientists yesterday continued hunting without success for signs of surface movement along a 30-mile segment of the San Andreas fault that ruptured deep in the earth Tuesday afternoon, causing wide damage in Northern California....

headline.main: Geologists Can't Find Quake's Surface Signs
